name: RHYTHM OF THE UNIVERSE
description:
Handpainted. The earth goddess holds the universe in her hands and plays a rhythm to heal and nurture. The natural world is represented by the bird on her shoulder who is witness to life and people. The bare breasts symbolise the incredible sustaining and nurturing qualities the earth can bring us and the radiant colours remind us that in our darkest times there is still colour and energy ready for us when we have the space to embrace it and use it for healing also. 

By Cat Brown, 2021
